Registration Fees

Students whose 2nd or 3rd English language course finished on or after 1st July wishing to avail of this bridging permission will be fee-exempt. (Applications made via ISDs online portal will have the fee refunded when the application is processed).

Students whose 3rd English language course finished prior to 1st July wishing to avail of this bridging permission will pay the standard fee of €300.

Students who avail of this bridging permission will be required to renew their immigration permission prior to the bridging permission expiring on 30th September 2025.
